#: libraries/classes/Config/Descriptions.php:62
msgid ""
"If enabled, user can enter any MySQL server in login form for cookie auth."
msgstr ""
"ຫາກເປີດໃຊ້, ຜູ້ໃຊ້ສາມາດປ້ອນ MySQL ເຊີເວີໃດກໍໄດ້ໃນຟອມເຂົ້າສູ່ລະບົບສຳລັບການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນດ້ວຍຄຸກກີ້."

#: libraries/classes/Config/Descriptions.php:64
msgid "Allow login to any MySQL server"
msgstr "ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ເຂົ້າສູ່ລະບົບ MySQL ເຊີເວີໃດກໍໄດ້"

#: libraries/classes/Config/Descriptions.php:67
msgid ""
"Restricts the MySQL servers the user can enter when a login to an arbitrary "
"MySQL server is enabled by matching the IP or hostname of the MySQL server "
"to the given regular expression."
msgstr ""
"ຈຳກັດ MySQL ເຊີເວີທີ່ຜູ້ໃຊ້ສາມາດປ້ອນໄດ້ ເມື່ອເປີດໃຊ້ການເຂົ້າສູ່ລະບົບແບບກຳນົດເອງ ໂດຍການປຽບທຽບ IP "
"ຫຼື ຊື່ໂຮສຂອງ MySQL ເຊີເວີ ກັບ regular expression ທີ່ກຳນົດ."

#: libraries/classes/Config/Descriptions.php:72
msgid "Restrict login to MySQL server"
msgstr "ຈຳກັດການເຂົ້າສູ່ລະບົບ MySQL ເຊີເວີ"

#: libraries/classes/Config/Descriptions.php:75
msgid ""
"Enabling this allows a page located on a different domain to call phpMyAdmin "
"inside a frame, and is a potential [strong]security hole[/strong] allowing "
"cross-frame scripting (XSS) attacks."
msgstr ""
"ການເປີດໃຊ້ສິ່ງນີ້ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ໜ້າເວັບໃນໂດເມນອື່ນເອີ້ນໃຊ້ phpMyAdmin ພາຍໃນເຟຣມໄດ້, ຊຶ່ງອາດເປັນ "
"[strong]ຊ່ອງໂຫວ່ດ້ານຄວາມປອດໄພ[/strong] ທີ່ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ມີການໂຈມຕີແບບ cross-frame "
"scripting (XSS)."

#: libraries/classes/Config/Descriptions.php:80
msgid "Allow third party framing"
msgstr "ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ໃຊ້ເຟຣມຈາກພາຍນອກ"

