"ບ FALSE. ຄ່າທີ່ບໍ່ແມ່ນສູນ = true."

#: libraries/classes/Plugins/Transformations/Abs/DateFormatTransformationsPlugin.php:30
msgid ""
"Displays a TIME, TIMESTAMP, DATETIME or numeric unix timestamp column as "
"formatted date. The first option is the offset (in hours) which will be "
"added to the timestamp (Default: 0). Use second option to specify a "
"different date/time format string. Third option determines whether you want "
"to see local date or UTC one (use \"local\" or \"utc\" strings) for that. "
"According to that, date format has different value - for \"local\" see the "
"documentation for PHP's strftime() function and for \"utc\" it is done using "
"gmdate() function."
msgstr ""
"ສະແດງຄໍລຳ TIME, TIMESTAMP, DATETIME ຫຼື ເລກ unix timestamp ໃນຮູບແບບວັນທີ. ຕົວເລືອກທຳອິ"
"ດແມ່ນຄ່າຊົດເຊີຍເວລາ (ເປັນຊົ່ວໂມງ) ທີ່ຈະເພີ່ມເຂົ້າໃນ timestamp (ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ: 0). ໃຊ້ຕົວເລືອກທີສອງເພື່ອລ"
"ະບຸຮູບແບບວັນທີ/ເວລາ. ຕົວເລືອກທີສາມກຳນົດວ່າເຈົ້າຕ້ອງການເບິ່ງວັນທີທ້ອງຖິ່ນ ຫຼື UTC (ໃຊ້ຂໍ້ຄວາມ "
"\"local\" ຫຼື \"utc\"). ຮູບແບບວັນທີຈະແຕກຕ່າງກັນໄປ - ສຳລັບ \"local\" ໃຫ້ເບິ່ງເອກະສານຂອງຟັງ"
"ຊັນ strftime() ຂອງ PHP ແລະ ສຳລັບ \"utc\" ຈະໃຊ້ຟັງຊັນ gmdate()."

#. l10n: See https://www.php.net/manual/en/function.strftime.php
#: libraries/classes/Plugins/Transformations/Abs/DateFormatTransformationsPlugin.php:62
#: libraries/classes/Util.php:1522
msgid "%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p"
msgstr "%B %d, %Y ເວລາ %I:%M %p"

#: libraries/classes/Plugins/Transformations/Abs/DownloadTransformationsPlugin.php:28
msgid ""
"Displays a link to download the binary data of the column. You can use the "
"first option to specify the filename, or use the second option as the name "
"of a column which contains the filename. If you use the second option, you "
"need to set the first option to the empty string."
msgstr ""
"ສະແດງລິ້ງເພື່ອດາວໂຫລດຂໍ້ມູນໄບນາຣີຂອງຄໍລຳ. ເຈົ້າສາມາດໃຊ້ຕົວເລືອກທຳອິດເພື່ອລະບຸຊື່ໄຟລ໌, ຫຼື ໃຊ້ຕົວເລືອກທີສ"
"ອງເປັນຊື່ຂອງຄໍລຳທີ່ເກັບຊື່ໄຟລ໌. ຖ້າໃຊ້ຕົວເລືອກທີສອງ, ເຈົ້າຕ້ອງຕັ້ງຄ່າຕົວເລືອກທຳອິດໃຫ້ເປັນຂໍ້ຄວາມຫວ່າງ."

#: libraries/classes/Plugins/Transformations/Abs/ExternalTransformationsPlugin.php:28
msgid ""
"LINUX ONLY: Launches an external application and feeds it the column data "
"via standard input. Returns the standard output of the application. The "
"default is Tidy, to pretty-print HTML code. For security reasons, you have "
"to manually edit the file libraries/classes/Plugins/Transformations/Abs/"
"ExternalTransformationsPlugin.php and list the tools you want to make "
"available. The first option is then the number of the program you want to "
"use. The second option should be blank for historical reasons. The third "
"option, if set to 1, will convert the output using htmlspecialchars() "
"(Default 1). The fourth option, if set to 1, will prevent wrapping and "
"ensure that the output appears all on one line (Default 1)."
msgstr ""
"ສຳລັບ LINUX ເທົ່ານັ້ນ: ເອີ້ນໃຊ້ແອັບພລິເຄຊັນພາຍນອກ ແລະ ສົ່ງຂໍ້ມູນຄໍລຳໃຫ້ຜ່ານ standard input. ສົ່ງຄືນ"
"ຜົນລັດ standard output ຂອງແອັບພລິເຄຊັນ. ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ Tidy ເພື່ອຈັດຮູບແບບ HTML ໃຫ້ສວຍງາມ. "
"ເພື່ອຄວາມປອດໄພ, ເຈົ້າຕ້ອງແກ້ໄຂໄຟລ໌ libraries/classes/Plugins/Transformations/Abs/"
"ExternalTransformationsPlugin.php ດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ ແລະ ລະບຸເຄື່ອງມືທີ່ຕ້ອງການໃຫ້ໃຊ້ໄດ້. ຕົວເລືອກທ"
"ຳອິດແມ່ນໝາຍເລກໂປຣແກຣມທີ່ຕ້ອງການໃຊ້. ຕົວເລືອກທີສອງຄວນຫວ່າງໄວ້. ຕົວເລືອກທີສາມ ຖ້າຕັ້ງເປັນ 1 ຈະແປງ"
"ຜົນລັດໂດຍໃຊ້ htmlspecialchars() (ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ 1). ຕົວເລືອກທີສີ່ ຖ້າຕັ້ງເປັນ 1 ຈະປ້ອງກັນການຂຶ້ນແຖວໃໝ່ເ"
"ພື່ອໃຫ້ຜົນລັດສະແດງໃນແຖວດຽວ (ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ 1)."

#: libraries/classes/Plugins/Transformations/Abs/ExternalTransformationsPlugin.php:114
#, possible-php-format
msgid ""
"You are using the external transformation command line options field, which "
"has been deprecated for security reasons. Add all command line options "
"directly to the definition in %s."
msgstr ""
"ເຈົ້າກຳລັງໃຊ້ຊ່ອງຕົວເລືອກ command line ສຳລັບການແປງຂໍ້ມູນພາຍນອກ, ເຊິ່ງຖືກຍົກເລີກການໃຊ້ງານແລ້ວເພື່ອ"
"ຄວາມປອດໄພ. ໃຫ້ເພີ່ມຕົວເລືອກ command line ທັງໝົດລົງໃນຄຳນິຍາມໃນ %s ໂດຍກົງ."

#: libraries/classes/Plugins/Transformations/Abs/FormattedTransformationsPlugin.php:28
msgid ""
"Displays the contents of the column as-is, without running it through "
"htmlspecialchars(). That is, the column is assumed to contain valid HTML."
msgstr ""
"ສະແດງເນື້ອໃນຂອງຄໍລຳຕາມສະພາບເດີມ, ໂດຍບໍ່ຜ່ານ htmlspecialchars(). ນັ້ນໝາຍຄວາມວ່າ ຄໍລຳນັ້ນຈະຖື"
"ກຖືວ່າປະກອບດ້ວຍ HTML ທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງ."

#: libraries/classes/Plugins/Transformations/Abs/HexTransformationsPlugin.php:28
msgid ""
"Displays hexadecimal representation of data. Optional first parameter "
"specifies how often space will be added (defaults to 2 nibbles)."
msgstr ""
"ສະແດງຂໍ້ມູນໃນຮູບແບບເລກຖານສິບຫົກ. ພາຣາມິເຕີທຳອິດ (ຖ້າໃສ່) ຈະກຳນົດວ່າຈະໃຫ້ເພີ່ມຍະຫວ່າງທຸກໆຈັກຕົວອັກສ"
"ອນ (ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ 2 nibbles)."

#: libraries/classes/Plugins/Transformations/Abs/ImageLinkTransformationsPlugin.php:32
msgid "Displays a link to download this image."
msgstr "ສະແດງລິ້ງເພື່ອດາວໂຫລດຮູບພາບນີ້."

#: libraries/classes/Plugins/Transformations/Abs/ImageUploadTransformationsPlugin.php:28
msgid ""
"Image upload functionality which also displays a thumbnail. The options are "
"the width and height of the thumbnail in pixels. Defaults to 100 X 100."
msgstr ""
"ຟັງຊັນອັບໂຫລດຮູບພາບເຊິ່ງຈະສະແດງຮູບຕົວຢ່າງ (Thumbnail) ນຳ. ຕົວເລືອກແມ່ນຄວາມກວ້າງ ແລະ ຄວາມສູງ"
"ຂອງຮູບຕົວຢ່າງເປັນພິກເຊລ. ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນ 100 X 100."

#: libraries/classes/Plugins/Transformations/Abs/ImageUploadTransformationsPlugin.php:87
msgid "Image preview here"
msgstr "ສະແດງຕົວຢ່າງຮູບພາບຢູ່ທີ່ນີ້"

#: libraries/classes/Plugins/Transformations/Abs/InlineTransformationsPlugin.php:32
msgid ""
"Displays a clickable thumbnail. The options are the maximum width and height "
"in pixels. The original aspect ratio is preserved."
msgstr ""
"ສະແດງຮູບຕົວຢ່າງທີ່ສາມາດຄລິກໄດ້. ຕົວເລືອກແມ່ນຄວາມກວ້າງ ແລະ ຄວາມສູງສູງສຸດເປັນພິກເຊລ. ໂດຍຈະຍັງຄົງຮັ"
"ກສາສັດສ່ວນເດີມຂອງຮູບໄວ້."

#: libraries/classes/Plugins/Transformations/Abs/LongToIPv4TransformationsPlugin.php:29
msgid ""
"Converts an (IPv4) Internet network address stored as a BIGINT into a string "
"in Internet standard dotted format."
msgstr ""
"ແປງທີ່ຢູ່ເຄືອຂ່າຍອິນເຕີເນັດ (IPv4) ທີ່ເກັບເປັນ BIGINT ໃຫ້ເປັນຂໍ້ຄວາມໃນຮູບແບບມາດຕະຖານອິນເຕີເນັດທີ່ມີຈຸດ"
"ຂັ້ນ."

#: libraries/classes/Plugins/Transformations/Abs/PreApPendTransformationsPlugin.php:29
msgid ""
"Prepends and/or Appends text to a string. First option is text to be "
"prepended, second is appended (enclosed in single quotes, default empty "
"string)."
msgstr ""
"ເພີ່ມຂໍ້ຄວາມໃສ່ທາງໜ້າ ແລະ/ຫຼື ທາງຫຼັງຂອງຂໍ້ຄວາມ. ຕົວເລືອກທຳອິດແມ່ນຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຈະເພີ່ມທາງໜ້າ, ທີສອງແມ່ນທາ"
"ງຫຼັງ (ຄຸມດ້ວຍເຄື່ອງໝາຍຄຳເວົ້າດ່ຽວ, ຄ່າເລີ່ມຕົ້ນແມ່ນຫວ່າງເປົ່າ)."

#: libraries/classes/Plugins/Transformations/Abs/RegexValidationTransformationsPlugin.php:30
msgid ""
"Validates the string using regular expression and performs insert only if "
"string matches it. The first option is the Regular Expression."
msgstr ""
"ກວດສອບຂໍ້ຄວາມໂດຍໃຊ້ Regular Expression ແລະ ຈະແຊກຂໍ້ມູນໄດ້ກໍຕໍ່ເມື່ອຂໍ້ຄວາມກົງກັບຮູບແບບເທົ່ານັ້ນ. ຕົ"
"ວເລືອກທຳອິດແມ່ນ Regular Expression."

#: libraries/classes/Plugins/Transformations/Abs/RegexValidationTransformationsPlugin.php:52
#, possible-php-format
msgid "Validation failed for the input string %s."
msgstr "ການກວດສອບຄວາມຖືກຕ້ອງລົ້ມເຫຼວສຳລັບຂໍ້ຄວາມ %s."

#: libraries/classes/Plugins/Transformations/Abs/SQLTransformationsPlugin.php:29
msgid "Formats text as SQL query with syntax highlighting."
msgstr ""
"ຈັດຮູບແບບຂໍ້ຄວາມເປັນຄຳສັ່ງ SQL ພ້ອມທັງສະແດງສີໄວຍາກອນ (Syntax highlighting)."

#: libraries/classes/Plugins/Transformations/Abs/SubstringTransformationsPlugin.php:28
msgid ""
"Displays a part of a string. The first option is the number of characters to "
"skip from the beginning of the string (Default 0). The second option is the "
"number of characters to return (Default: until end of string). The third "
"option is the string to append and/or prepend when truncation occurs "
"(Default: \"…\")."
msgstr ""
"ສະແດງບາງສ່ວນຂອງຂໍ້ຄວາມ. ຕົວເລືອກທຳອິດແມ່ນຈຳນວນຕົວອັກສອນທີ່ຈະຂ້າມຈາກຕອນຕົ້ນ (ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ 0). ຕົວເລືອ"
"ກທີສອງແມ່ນຈຳນວນຕົວອັກສອນທີ່ຈະສະແດງ (ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ: ຈົນຈົບຂໍ້ຄວາມ). ຕົວເລືອກທີສາມແມ່ນຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ຈະເພີ່ມໃສ່ທາ"
"ງໜ້າ ຫຼື ທາງຫຼັງ ເມື່ອມີການຕັດຂໍ້ຄວາມ (ເລີ່ມຕົ້ນ: \"…\")."

#: libraries/classes/Plugins/Transformations/Abs/TextFileUploadTransformationsPlugin.php:30
msgid ""
"File upload functionality for TEXT columns. It does not have a textarea for "
"input."
msgstr ""
"ຟັງຊັນອັບໂຫລດໄຟລ໌ສຳລັບຄໍລຳ TEXT. ເຊິ່ງຈະບໍ່ມີຊ່ອງປ້ອນຂໍ້ຄວາມ (Textarea)."

#: libraries/classes/Plugins/Transformations/Abs/TextImageLinkTransformationsPlugin.php:33
msgid ""
"Displays an image and a link; the column contains the filename. The first "
"option is a URL prefix like \"https://www.example.com/\". The second and "
"third options are the width and the height in pixels."
msgstr ""
"ສະແດງຮູບພາບ ແລະ ລິ້ງ; ໂດຍທີ່ຄໍລຳນັ້ນຈະເກັບຊື່ໄຟລ໌. ຕົວເລືອກທຳອິດແມ່ນ URL ນຳໜ້າ ເຊັ່ນ \"https://"
"www.example.com/\". ຕົວເລືອກທີສອງ ແລະ ສາມແມ່ນຄວາມກວ້າງ ແລະ ຄວາມສູງເປັນພິກເຊລ."

#: libraries/classes/Plugins/Transformations/Abs/TextLinkTransformationsPlugin.php:33
msgid ""
"Displays a link; the column contains the filename. The first option is a URL "
"prefix like \"https://www.example.com/\". The second option is a title for "
"the link."
msgstr ""
"ສະແດງລິ້ງ; ໂດຍທີ່ຄໍລຳນັ້ນຈະເກັບຊື່ໄຟລ໌. ຕົວເລືອກທຳອິດແມ່ນ URL ນຳໜ້າ ເຊັ່ນ \"https://"
"www.example.com/\". ຕົວເລືອກທີສອງແມ່ນຫົວຂໍ້ຂອງລິ້ງ."

